-- International Petroleum Investment Co. to Meet Bond Investors
-- B y   S t e f a n i a   B i a n c h i   a n d   C a r o l i n e   H y d e
-- 2010-10-28T11:13:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-28/international-petroleum-of-abu-dhabi-hires-banks-to-meet-bond-investors.html
International Petroleum Investment
Co. plans to meet bond investors in the United Arab Emirates,
Asia, Europe and the U.S. starting Oct. 31, according to two
people with knowledge of the roadshow.  Goldman Sachs Group Inc., Bank of America Corp., HSBC
Holdings Plc, National Bank of Abu Dhabi, Standard Chartered
Bank and Royal Bank of Scotland Group Plc are arranging the
meetings, the people said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stefania Bianchi in Dubai at 
 sbianchi10@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Caroline Hyde at 
 chyde3@bloomberg.net  